      "instruction": "<p>Trim, then slice your<strong> spring onion[s]</strong></p><p>Peel and roughly chop your <strong>garlic</strong></p><p>Cut your <strong>red chilli[es]</strong> in half lengthways, deseed (scrape the seeds out with a teaspoon) and chop finely</p><p>Chop your <strong>coriander</strong> finely, including the stalks, keeping the leaves and stalks separate</p>",
      "order": 2,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
