    {
      "instruction": "<p>Heat a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick) with 1/2 tbsp<span class=\"text-purple\"> [3/4 tbsp]</span><span class=\"text-danger\"> [1 tbsp]</span> <strong>vegetable oil</strong> over a medium-high heat</p><p>Once hot, add your <strong>free</strong> <strong>range</strong> <strong>chicken breast portion[s]</strong><span class=\"text-danger\"> </span>and cook for 3 min on each side or until browned</p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
        "images": [
