      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once browned, add the <strong>Thai-style paste</strong> to the chicken and cook for 2-3 min further or until fragrant</p><p>Once fragrant, reduce the heat to medium, add the <strong>coconut stock </strong>and cook for 10-12 min or until the chicken is cooked through (no pink meat!) and the sauce has thickened</p><p>Add the juice of <strong>half </strong>your <strong>lime[s]</strong> and stir it all together – this is your <strong>Thai-style sauce</strong></p><p>Cut the <strong>remaining lime</strong> into 1 wedge per person</p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
