    {
      "instruction": "<p>Slice the<strong> Thai-style free range chicken </strong>finely and serve with the <strong>brown rice</strong> and<strong> gingery veg</strong> to the side</p><p>Drizzle the <strong>Thai-style sauce</strong> all over</p><p>Garnish with the <strong>chopped coriander leaves </strong>and a<strong> lime wedge</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
